  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the social, emotional, physical, and educational
      effects of Girls First, a combined resilience and adolescent health program, vs. its
      components and a control group, among adolescents in India.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
